# NSFileHandleNotificationDataItem

**Global Variable**

A key in the userinfo dictionary in a [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/FileHandle/readCompletionNotification] and [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSNotification/Name-swift.struct/NSFileHandleReadToEndOfFileCompletion].

## Declaration

```swift
let NSFileHandleNotificationDataItem: String
```

## Discussion

The corresponding value is an `NSData` object containing the available data read from a socket connection.

## Constants

- **NSFileHandleNotificationFileHandleItem**: A key in the userinfo dictionary in a [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSNotification/Name-swift.struct/NSFileHandleConnectionAccepted] notification.
- **NSFileHandleNotificationMonitorModes**: Currently unused.
